{"tid":1968112,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解呢排咁多人吹捧it","createTime":"2020-04-11T12:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T12:55:31.000Z","uid":34235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f929f5e9eb63ffb9e757ad63ecfc085e541b3a0f","tid":1968112,"uid":34235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:08:12.000Z","msg":"成班人老點班後生話人工高好易入行乜乜乜，又拎外國做例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你地班仆街，呢度係香港，人工極低工時長，假期仲要花時間去進修<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時返工好少講嘢，女同事極少，成班又臭又毒嘅麻甩佬坐喺office度唔出聲對住部電腦，本身唔毒都變到毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我同公司班同事三十都未夠，壓力大到已經有少少脫髮跡象<br />\n<br />\n想入行，大家真係諗清楚先，唔好葬送未來幾十年嘅青春，人生苦短，及時行樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe4cef0f26300e402f8474f9bcdee50719cf37f","tid":1968112,"uid":148545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:26:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d770e8bc16dd9318f3fdc15cc71874ac8d8cf9","tid":1968112,"uid":34235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"efe4cef0f26300e402f8474f9bcdee50719cf37f","tid":1968112,"uid":148545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:26:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8156721f259464b84dada7d5f7a467a7a25e151d","tid":1968112,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gifrun.com/programs/temp/49cdbfa1074649a1b364074cc822cf21.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgifrun.com%2Fprograms%2Ftemp%2F49cdbfa1074649a1b364074cc822cf21.gif&h=2b0c7240&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1ec290f5a66c130627c94573d1